          "The art design that defines "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Healer’s Quest"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " has that hand drawn style, kind of like things moving around in a story book. It’s the kind of art design that suits the comedic aspect, highlighting some ridiculous slapstick from the party and in the background of fights. This is the kind of art design I can truly appreciate as it tends to allow for fun moments and will age a lot cleaner than those that take the realistic approach."
        ]
      ]
