          "Healer’s Quest"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " is a fun, light-hearted RPG that has quite a difficult challenge that involves trying to keep the party alive against the bumbling DPS and Tanks. It has a strong art style that emphasises the comedic aspect, however the music and the game’s world feel a bit more generic than one would hope. It does however contain an insightful look at the challenges that healers take on while being overshadowed by the rest of the party."
        ]
      ]
